<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='861538' id='t-861538'>to listen to different people,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='863042' id='t-863042'>to listen to President Carter --
90 years old, by the way,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='866312' id='t-866312'>and he we was throwing these figures
