<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='874301' id='t-874301'>He was rattling off --
I mean, that's amazing, I'm sorry.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:48
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='877931' id='t-877931'>PM: He's an amazing man.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
