<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='885501' id='t-885501'>who's a former president --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='887410' id='t-887410'>Thank you, Irish! 62 percent! LGBTQ! Yes!</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
