<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='933222' id='t-933222'>every single person's an influencer.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='935061' id='t-935061'>Never, ever forget that. OK?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='937603' id='t-937603'>So don't ever give up on yourself.</span>
